OL,3,CProlific blood donor may have saved up
OL,4,Cto 1,000 lives
OL,6,FA man from Somerset may have helped
OL,7,Fsave the lives of more than a thousand
OL,8,Fpeople after reaching a huge blood
OL,9,Fdonation milestone.
OL,11,FSteve Stone, who lives in Monkton
OL,12,FHeathfield near Taunton, recently gave
OL,13,Fhis 350th unit - thought to be one of
OL,14,Fthe highest number of donations in the
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FSteve's been regularly donating since
OL,18,Fthe 1980s and began when he "bunked
OL,19,Foff from college" with a friend.
