OL,3,CProlific blood donor may have saved up
OL,4,Cto 1,000 lives
OL,6,FHe said: "We got a morning off to go
OL,7,Fand give blood at Southmead. We were
OL,8,Fdoing something good and bunking off
OL,9,Fso it was worth doing!"
OL,11,FOver the years Steve has donated
OL,12,Fblood, plasma and platelets. He also
OL,13,Fencourages more people to donate when
OL,14,Fthey can.
OL,16,FHe said: "Three out of four of my
OL,17,Fdaughters work for the NHS, my wife
OL,18,Fhad a transfusion when the eldest was
OL,19,Fborn - it is worth it. It's got to be
OL,20,Fthere in case they can save a life."
