OL,3,CProlific blood donor may have saved up
OL,4,Cto 1,000 lives
OL,6,FTracey Alford, NHS Blood and
OL,7,FTransplant's Senior Sister for the
OL,8,FTaunton Team, said: "We'd like to
OL,9,Fcongratulate and thank Steve for his
OL,10,Fincredible dedication and commitment
OL,11,Fto reach 350 whole blood and platelet
OL,12,Fdonations.
OL,14,F"Every donation can help up to three
OL,15,Fpeople, Steve's selfless generosity
OL,16,Fcould have helped save the lives of
OL,17,Fmore than 1,000 seriously ill
OL,18,Fpatients."
OL,20,FLearn more about giving blood.
